Which Pirates of the Caribbean character are you?

You're Captain Jack Sparrow! Played by Johnny Depp, you're a daft pirate with no regard for laws. Your crimes include piracy, smuggling, impersonating an officer of the Spanish Royal Navy, impersonating a cleric of the Church of England, and very many others. You can't usually make up your mind which side you're fighting for, and you enjoy really bad eggs.

Which Disney heroine are you?

YOU ARE: Meg (Hercules). Somebody really hurt you in the past, and you're jaded and cynical. You're ruthless in pursuit of your goals, and you're shutting everyone out who wants to help you. You need a sweet, genuine, naive hero who'll help you to realize that they all aren't bad. Until then, your wit and sex appeal will only get you so far.

Which Tim Burton character are you?
You are Emily, the Corpse Bride. You were once in love but your mate abandoned you and left you for "dead". But you have found someone else and you want him/her to love you and stay by your side. You love to play around and have a good time. Everyone you know really likes you, and you're popular for your looks and personality. You don't get sad too often, but when you do, you cry your eyes out.
